creator: EventBank
descriptionHtml:
The Economist Corporate Network app gives you a new way to engage, network and receive important information about your events, memberships and more. Get the most out of your events and maximize your membership benefits with an all-in-one engagement app. Please note: to gain access to our events, an existing ECN membership is required.

Key Community Engagement Features:
* Direct messaging
* Group chats & event rooms
* Digital business cards
* Personal CRM for all connections you make
* Contact profile

Key Event Features:
* Fast event registration and payment processing
* Easy check-in with QR codes
* Quick access to all event information including agendas, venues, speaker bios, session presentations, and ticketing
* Preview and register for upcoming events that match your interests
* Social media integration for easy sharing

Key Membership Features:
* Direct access to organization newsletters, announcements, and upcoming events
* Mobile membership directories so you can expand your network
* Member profile and membership renewal management
* Virtual membership cards to leverage all your membership benefits
descriptionShort: The ultimate mobile hub for ECN events and membership experience.

Get the most out of your events and maximize your membership benefits with an all-in-one engagement app. Please note: to gain access to our events, an existing Corporate Network membership is required.

Key Community Engagement Features:
* Direct messaging
* Group chats & event rooms
* Digital business cards
* Personal CRM for all connections you make
* Contact profile

Key Event Features:
* Fast event registration and payment processing
* Easy check-in with QR codes
* Quick access to all event information including agendas, venues, speaker bios, session presentations, and ticketing
* Preview and register for upcoming events that match your interests
* Social media integration for easy sharing

Key Membership Features:
* Direct access to organization newsletters, announcements, and upcoming events
* Mobile membership directories so you can expand your network
* Member profile and membership renewal management
* Virtual membership cards to leverage all your membership benefits
descriptionShort: The ultimate mobile hub for Corporate Network events and membership experience.
